headline.print_headline: World Trade Center Complex on Way to Completion
headline.main: World Trade Center Complex on Way to Completion

lead_paragraph: Thirteen years after 9/11 forever changed the New York skyline, officials say most work at the World Trade Center complex is on track and on budget.
